channel.title: Proxies, proxies, proxies!
channel.description:
[size=72pt]ARGH![/size]
I'm writing this post in a state of frustration, Because proxie's aren't accessable, quick, for the nation. I need one for my site, Because my school's shite, And blocks the keyword 'masturbation'!
To cut a long story short, At I first I had thought, That getting a proxy'd be easy, Then I found out, With a scream and a shout, That the scripts available are sleezy!
I need a good code, So my classmates can be showed, Myspace, and facebook, and such, The only one we can access right now, Translates all the pages into dutch!
So I need all your advice, And please, just be nice, I need help to find a good script. I don't care where it's from, I just need to get on, Find me one, I don't care if it's ripped!
I looked all on google, It left my mind bamboozled, Maybe I'm just being a fool. But I can't find one right, The search results were all shite, Please help me, get on games, at school!
You probably need more detail than this, But please be assured, I'm not taking the piss, I need a simple proxy, A small html boxy, To be embedded into this;
http://irloling.ulmb.com/maths.htm
You'll notice when you open, That link, the form is broken, So help me! I'm begging you! Please! Find me a script, That'll get that form fixed, And you may be rewarded, with a small fee!
